      "content": "The SIGINT intercepts are being thoroughly analyzed to distinguish between operational chatter and genuine threat indicators. While some communications exhibit a level of organization, it is not yet conclusive proof of a large-scale military buildup. We are currently cross-referencing these signals with ground reports to confirm the intent behind the activity, and a deeper dive into the encryption keys is underway. I will provide a definitive update the moment the analysts can confirm a pattern of hostile intent.",
      "source": "target",
